	<string name="notationText">A turn of layer is written by adding a suffix to the face\'s name. All moves should be applied as if you were looking at the face straight-on. Using the U face as an example here are all three cases:\n\nU - A 90-degree clockwise turn.\nU\' - A 90-degree counterclockwise turn.\nU2 - A 180-degree turn.</string>

